* June 12, 1986, Del Rey, paperback, 189 pages, 
* January 1, 1971, Ace, paperback, 189 pages
* September 26, 2006, Del Rey, paperback, 256 pages, 
* December 2008, Virginia Edition (Vol. 12), hardcover, 171 pages, 

