<text>The Robert Heinlein Omnibus is an anthology of science fiction published in 1958, containing a novel, a novella and a short story by American writer Robert A. Heinlein:
* &quot;Beyond This Horizon&quot; (1942)
* &quot;The Man Who Sold The Moon&quot; (1950)
